Politics is expected to dominate on Saturday at Naitiri area in Tongaren constituency during the burial of area MP Eseli Simiyu&rsquo;s mother. Rebecca Nasimiyu died last week at the Moi Teaching and Referal Hospital in Eldoret. She was 80 and had been in a coma. County and national leaders have sent condolences to Eseli, the Ford Kenya secretary general. NASA flagbearer Raila Odinga, running mate Kalonzo Musyoka and co-principal Moses Wetang&rsquo;ula a are expected to attend. The NASA brigade will be visting Western for the first time since unveiling its presidential line-up on April 27at Uhuru Park, Nairobi .The line-up was criticised by some members of the Mulembe nation, with some saying the Luhyas got a raw deal.